column11:
To quantify river plastic transport and composition in the Cisadane, rivers with data to be
collected for 6 months: October to April 2022. The tasks to be executed by Contractor and
supported by Principal could be defined:
1. Visual counting and classification of floating debris in the Cisadane river 5 days per
month (data to be used for sensor validation);
2. Coordinate the installation of river monitoring equipment with local installation
partners and permitting authorities.
3. Collect data hydraulic data from relevant local authorities (BBWS) namely water level
data at Kali Baru bridge.
4. The Contractor will make available personnel to be responsible for coordinating the
installation, light maintenance and troubleshooting of the Obscape River Monitoring
Systems and time lapse camera sensors installed by the Principal, such as lens
cleaning, cable connections, update settings, etc.
column12:
Deliverables
1. Time series of visually counted plastic debris and the flow velocity on the Cisadane
river 5 days a month for 6 months with a temporal resolution of one hour between
the measurements. Plastic composition data according to The Ocean Cleanup
Classification protocol.
2. Installation of 4 Permanent Obscape RMS cameras for at least 12 months on the Kali
Baru bridges over the Cisadane.
3. Installation of 1 permanent Obscape time lapse camera at a to be defined location
on along the Cisadane in proximity to proposed Interceptor deployment site.

column12:
PILOT
rumah tangga: untuk pengumpulan, kami akan melayani 1.898 rumah dan menargetkan 75% rumah tangga yang kami layani akan menggunakan aplikasi bank plastik dalam sistem pengumpulan sampah mereka
bank sampah: untuk pengumpulannya, kami akan melayani 193 bank sampah dan menargetkan 75% dari 193 bank sampah akan menggunakan aplikasi Plastic Bank dalam sistem pengumpulan sampah mereka

PENERAPAN
(1) mencapai 100 ton sampah plastik yang dikumpulkan selama program (2) 75% dari total rumah tangga dan bank sampah terus menggunakan aplikasi (3) tingkat pemilahan meningkat di atas 35% (dibandingkan dengan tingkat pemilahan saat ini) (4) rumah tangga sekitar di luar TKR mengumpulkan sampah yang dapat didaur ulang ke bank sampah terdekat (5) bank sampah yang dibantu dalam program ini akan mengalami peningkatan yang signifikan dalam anggotanya, yang juga meningkatkan sampah yang dikumpulkan (6) peningkatan manajemen data sistem pengumpulan sampah

column11:
To quantify river plastic transport and composition in the Cisadane, rivers with data to be
collected for 6 months: October to April 2022. The tasks to be executed by Contractor and
supported by Principal could be defined:
1. Visual counting and classification of floating debris in the Cisadane river 5 days per
month (data to be used for sensor validation);
2. Coordinate the installation of river monitoring equipment with local installation
partners and permitting authorities.
3. Collect data hydraulic data from relevant local authorities (BBWS) namely water level
data at Kali Baru bridge.
4. The Contractor will make available personnel to be responsible for coordinating the
installation, light maintenance and troubleshooting of the Obscape River Monitoring
Systems and time lapse camera sensors installed by the Principal, such as lens
cleaning, cable connections, update settings, etc.
column12:
Deliverables
1. Time series of visually counted plastic debris and the flow velocity on the Cisadane
river 5 days a month for 6 months with a temporal resolution of one hour between
the measurements. Plastic composition data according to The Ocean Cleanup
Classification protocol.
2. Installation of 4 Permanent Obscape RMS cameras for at least 12 months on the Kali
Baru bridges over the Cisadane.
3. Installation of 1 permanent Obscape time lapse camera at a to be defined location
on along the Cisadane in proximity to proposed Interceptor deployment site.

column12:
PILOT
rumah tangga: untuk pengumpulan, kami akan melayani 1.898 rumah dan menargetkan 75% rumah tangga yang kami layani akan menggunakan aplikasi bank plastik dalam sistem pengumpulan sampah mereka
bank sampah: untuk pengumpulannya, kami akan melayani 193 bank sampah dan menargetkan 75% dari 193 bank sampah akan menggunakan aplikasi Plastic Bank dalam sistem pengumpulan sampah mereka

PENERAPAN
(1) mencapai 100 ton sampah plastik yang dikumpulkan selama program (2) 75% dari total rumah tangga dan bank sampah terus menggunakan aplikasi (3) tingkat pemilahan meningkat di atas 35% (dibandingkan dengan tingkat pemilahan saat ini) (4) rumah tangga sekitar di luar TKR mengumpulkan sampah yang dapat didaur ulang ke bank sampah terdekat (5) bank sampah yang dibantu dalam program ini akan mengalami peningkatan yang signifikan dalam anggotanya, yang juga meningkatkan sampah yang dikumpulkan (6) peningkatan manajemen data sistem pengumpulan sampah

column11:
To quantify river plastic transport and composition in the Cisadane, rivers with data to be
collected for 6 months: October to April 2022. The tasks to be executed by Contractor and
supported by Principal could be defined:
1. Visual counting and classification of floating debris in the Cisadane river 5 days per
month (data to be used for sensor validation);
2. Coordinate the installation of river monitoring equipment with local installation
partners and permitting authorities.
3. Collect data hydraulic data from relevant local authorities (BBWS) namely water level
data at Kali Baru bridge.
4. The Contractor will make available personnel to be responsible for coordinating the
installation, light maintenance and troubleshooting of the Obscape River Monitoring
Systems and time lapse camera sensors installed by the Principal, such as lens
cleaning, cable connections, update settings, etc.
column12:
Deliverables
1. Time series of visually counted plastic debris and the flow velocity on the Cisadane
river 5 days a month for 6 months with a temporal resolution of one hour between
the measurements. Plastic composition data according to The Ocean Cleanup
Classification protocol.
2. Installation of 4 Permanent Obscape RMS cameras for at least 12 months on the Kali
Baru bridges over the Cisadane.
3. Installation of 1 permanent Obscape time lapse camera at a to be defined location
on along the Cisadane in proximity to proposed Interceptor deployment site.

column12:
PILOT
rumah tangga: untuk pengumpulan, kami akan melayani 1.898 rumah dan menargetkan 75% rumah tangga yang kami layani akan menggunakan aplikasi bank plastik dalam sistem pengumpulan sampah mereka
bank sampah: untuk pengumpulannya, kami akan melayani 193 bank sampah dan menargetkan 75% dari 193 bank sampah akan menggunakan aplikasi Plastic Bank dalam sistem pengumpulan sampah mereka

PENERAPAN
(1) mencapai 100 ton sampah plastik yang dikumpulkan selama program (2) 75% dari total rumah tangga dan bank sampah terus menggunakan aplikasi (3) tingkat pemilahan meningkat di atas 35% (dibandingkan dengan tingkat pemilahan saat ini) (4) rumah tangga sekitar di luar TKR mengumpulkan sampah yang dapat didaur ulang ke bank sampah terdekat (5) bank sampah yang dibantu dalam program ini akan mengalami peningkatan yang signifikan dalam anggotanya, yang juga meningkatkan sampah yang dikumpulkan (6) peningkatan manajemen data sistem pengumpulan sampah

column11:
To quantify river plastic transport and composition in the Cisadane, rivers with data to be
collected for 6 months: October to April 2022. The tasks to be executed by Contractor and
supported by Principal could be defined:
1. Visual counting and classification of floating debris in the Cisadane river 5 days per
month (data to be used for sensor validation);
2. Coordinate the installation of river monitoring equipment with local installation
partners and permitting authorities.
3. Collect data hydraulic data from relevant local authorities (BBWS) namely water level
data at Kali Baru bridge.
4. The Contractor will make available personnel to be responsible for coordinating the
installation, light maintenance and troubleshooting of the Obscape River Monitoring
Systems and time lapse camera sensors installed by the Principal, such as lens
cleaning, cable connections, update settings, etc.
column12:
Deliverables
1. Time series of visually counted plastic debris and the flow velocity on the Cisadane
river 5 days a month for 6 months with a temporal resolution of one hour between
the measurements. Plastic composition data according to The Ocean Cleanup
Classification protocol.
2. Installation of 4 Permanent Obscape RMS cameras for at least 12 months on the Kali
Baru bridges over the Cisadane.
3. Installation of 1 permanent Obscape time lapse camera at a to be defined location
on along the Cisadane in proximity to proposed Interceptor deployment site.

PILOT
rumah tangga: untuk pengumpulan, kami akan melayani 1.898 rumah dan menargetkan 75% rumah tangga yang kami layani akan menggunakan aplikasi bank plastik dalam sistem pengumpulan sampah mereka

column11:
To quantify river plastic transport and composition in the Cisadane, rivers with data to be
collected for 6 months: October to April 2022. The tasks to be executed by Contractor and
supported by Principal could be defined:
1. Visual counting and classification of floating debris in the Cisadane river 5 days per
month (data to be used for sensor validation);
2. Coordinate the installation of river monitoring equipment with local installation
partners and permitting authorities.
3. Collect data hydraulic data from relevant local authorities (BBWS) namely water level
data at Kali Baru bridge.
4. The Contractor will make available personnel to be responsible for coordinating the
installation, light maintenance and troubleshooting of the Obscape River Monitoring
Systems and time lapse camera sensors installed by the Principal, such as lens
cleaning, cable connections, update settings, etc.
column12:
Deliverables
1. Time series of visually counted plastic debris and the flow velocity on the Cisadane
river 5 days a month for 6 months with a temporal resolution of one hour between
the measurements. Plastic composition data according to The Ocean Cleanup
Classification protocol.
2. Installation of 4 Permanent Obscape RMS cameras for at least 12 months on the Kali
Baru bridges over the Cisadane.
3. Installation of 1 permanent Obscape time lapse camera at a to be defined location
on along the Cisadane in proximity to proposed Interceptor deployment site.

column12:
PILOT
rumah tangga: untuk pengumpulan, kami akan melayani 1.898 rumah dan menargetkan 75% rumah tangga yang kami layani akan menggunakan aplikasi bank plastik dalam sistem pengumpulan sampah mereka
bank sampah: untuk pengumpulannya, kami akan melayani 193 bank sampah dan menargetkan 75% dari 193 bank sampah akan menggunakan aplikasi Plastic Bank dalam sistem pengumpulan sampah mereka

PENERAPAN
(1) mencapai 100 ton sampah plastik yang dikumpulkan selama program (2) 75% dari total rumah tangga dan bank sampah terus menggunakan aplikasi (3) tingkat pemilahan meningkat di atas 35% (dibandingkan dengan tingkat pemilahan saat ini) (4) rumah tangga sekitar di luar TKR mengumpulkan sampah yang dapat didaur ulang ke bank sampah terdekat (5) bank sampah yang dibantu dalam program ini akan mengalami peningkatan yang signifikan dalam anggotanya, yang juga meningkatkan sampah yang dikumpulkan (6) peningkatan manajemen data sistem pengumpulan sampah
